[SN]TITLE[SN]
Rugby World Cup referee Nigel Owens' Swansea uni honour

[SN]FIRST-SENTENCE[SN]
Rugby World Cup final referee Nigel Owens has received an honorary degree from Swansea University.

[SN]RESTBODY[SN]
Mr Owens, of Mynyddcerrig in Carmarthenshire, received an honorary LLD (Doctor of Laws) from the College of Law.
He said he was "humbled" to be given the accolade at a ceremony on Monday.
Theatre designer Sean Crowley, of the Royal Welsh College of Music and Drama, also became a Doctor of Letters.
